	Pitt gets a lift    
	 London, July 4 (PTI): Actor Brad Pitt had to be rescued by a photographer after his expensive custom-made motorbike broke down in a residential area of Los Angeles.      
	The Oceans Eleven star was enjoying a leisurely ride when it suddenly broke down. He tried his best to fix it but had to turn to a photographer following him for a ride back home, reports the Daily Mail.      
	The actor, who was dressed in jeans and shirt, was wearing a helmet with Daddys helmet scrawled on it.     
	Fox swipe    
	 London (PTI): Actress Megan Fox was at the receiving end of some harsh words when Transformers director Michael Bay called her ridiculous for publicly slamming the movie which launched her career. The 23-year old actress, who shot to fame with Transformers, took a swipe at the sequel in a new interview, describing it as not a movie about acting. Bay reacted by saying: Well, thats Megan Fox for you. She says some very ridiculous things because shes 23 years old and she still has a lot of growing to do.     
	Spider kid    
	 Los Angeles (PTI): Tobey Maguire has revealed the name of his second child. The boy, who was born in May, will be called Otis Tobias Maguire. While the babys second name matches that of Maguire, the reason for the first name wasnt revealed.                                                                                                                                                                        
